Type of Feat: Class
Specifics: For every 10% of his total hit points the primal fury has lost to damage he gains a +1 attack bonus (which counts against the +20 cap) as well as 2 points of bonus sonic damage. He suffers a 25% vulnerability to physical damage in this stance. For every 2 points of attack bonus he gains, he suffers a -1 AC penalty.
Use: Selected.